{"tid":1039068,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【自製圖表】德國極左翼定極右翼暴力啲？齊睇憲法保護局數據","createTime":"2019-02-27T07:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T13:21:53.000Z","uid":138409,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e75b9174796ae2478033d1d20df8a958ef6c1cb6","tid":1039068,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:13:53.000Z","msg":"最近心血來潮<br />\n睇咗一堆德國憲法保護局嘅報告summary （報告全文得德文，唔識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n2014-2017嘅報告：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.verfassungsschutz.de/en/public-relations/publications/annual-reports\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verfassungsschutz.de%2Fen%2Fpublic-relations%2Fpublications%2Fannual-reports&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hExj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=ae0daf37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.verfassungsschutz.de/en/public-relations/publications/annual-reports</a><br />\n2012: <a href=\"https://www.bmi.bund.de/SharedDocs/downloads/EN/publikationen/2013/vsb_kurzfassung_engl_2012.pdf?__blob=publicationFile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bmi.bund.de%2FSharedDocs%2Fdownloads%2FEN%2Fpublikationen%2F2013%2Fvsb_kurzfassung_engl_2012.pdf%3F__blob%3DpublicationFile&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hExj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=e8e54b0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bmi.bund.de/SharedDocs/downloads/EN/publikationen/2013/vsb_kurzfassung_engl_2012.pdf?__blob=publicationFile</a><br />\n因為每份報告都會recap返早一兩年嘅數據<br />\n所以基本上2011-2017嘅數據都有<br />\n（注意：德國聯邦刑事廳雖然有每年更新犯罪數據，但係因為左右翼罪行屬於「帶政治動機之刑事罪行」，所以按法律唔會包括響裡面）<br />\n<br />\n然後將資料整咗個Google excel form<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1oZrTuo4B95AXuutMlrC1sh5GFv4ofmd0pnl_JQoYDzw/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1oZrTuo4B95AXuutMlrC1sh5GFv4ofmd0pnl_JQoYDzw%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hExj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=4350f3ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1oZrTuo4B95AXuutMlrC1sh5GFv4ofmd0pnl_JQoYDzw/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係comparison:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>代表左翼<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色</span>代表右翼<br />\n<br />\n左右互片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ek8OnQj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEk8OnQj.png&h=b8ba30f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左定右暴力罪行多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFqhgaL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFqhgaL.png&h=42d6482b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊一邊（企圖）殺人多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSvUipy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSvUipy.png&h=24e10174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而最出乎意料嘅係<br />\n左定右犯罪率高啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ZuJWbB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZuJWbB.png&h=d49d1069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未來可能會整埋唔同極端團體嘅人數變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有巴打留意呢方面嘅消息都可以討論下啊"},{"pid":"125b9a5eda56646dc448fe0000779d79d40e6a68","tid":1039068,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1797582555dfc29fdb7625fd6cf7897571f3c5","tid":1039068,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f018d481ed78c04d6da009215b9e5f958128e652","tid":1039068,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi