e":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"點定義先 好似美國咁 阿豬阿狗都altright就完全無參考價值<br />\n例如殺人個表 如果佢地將啲自稱雅利安人嘅黑幫飛車黨放入去就完全無公信力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"所謂極端主義<br />\n係指衝擊德國「自由民主基本秩序」嘅思想<br />\n根據聯邦憲法法院嘅定義<br />\n包括如基本人權、民主制度、問責政府等元素<br />\n<br />\n具體執行上<br />\n憲法保護局會對懷疑團體搜集資料（派臥底、監聽etc）<br />\n假如有足夠證據證明其衝擊基本秩序<br />\n就會向憲法法院申請解散該政黨<br />\n如果係非政黨類別嘅結社組織<br />\n就由聯邦/地方政府宣布強制解散"},{"pid":"55029e9f9db4c5aa13f06398e2830743695a884e","tid":1039068,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T12:39:40.000Z","msg":"英文不錯"},{"pid":"ca2997e17ec419b3c95f2e2ed8ba67f6157ba85b","tid":1039068,"uid":176991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"16年發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反難民？"},{"pid":"42626195eb5f1ca6ef8dd773daa92622acf166dc","tid":1039068,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca2997e17ec419b3c95f2e2ed8ba67f6157ba85b","tid":1039068,"uid":176991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"16年發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反難民？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource: Brief summary--2016 Report on the Protection of the Constitution: Facts and Trends<br />\np.7<br />\n<blockquote>The number of violent right-wing extremist crimes with a xenophobic background rose once again; the percentage of violent criminal offences <span style=\"color: red;\">against accommodation centres for asylum applicants</span> remained at the high level of 2015.<br />\n...<br />\nAt 1,190, the number of violent crimes <span style=\"color: red;\">directed at foreigners</span>(2015: 918) was the highest since the current definition of politically motivated crime was introduced in 2001.</blockquote>"}]}